{"tid":1330094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】逾30名7.1衝擊立法會示威者抵台灣尋庇護 傳已接觸陸委會","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:27:06.000Z","uid":4783,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"59b516217c0172eacf8d7e92516c9699d7a6a206","tid":1330094,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"建立時間 (HKT): 0718 19:58<br />\n<br />\n7.1當晚示威者闖入及破壞立法會大樓，示威者或需面對警方追捕及法律責任。本報接獲可靠消息，逃往台灣的示威者人數逾30人，均為曾經參與7.1衝擊立法會行動的學生，他們事後沒有被捕，抵台後已接觸當地官方機構。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台亦有報道，有示威者已抵達台灣尋求庇護。報道中引述一名不願透露姓名的台灣律師，指衝擊立法會後，陸續有示威者抵台，正與陸委會接觸，尋求庇護。該名律師表示，由於該批示威者尚未被捕或檢控，衝擊時亦戴上口罩，難以證明自己曾經參與行動，因此他們要延長居台期限，技術上可能遇上困難。<br />\n<br />\n本報正就事件向保安局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190718/59838175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59838175&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=d9b0a96d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59838175&h=af55831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190718/59838175</a>"},{"pid":"2c87b490148a0a19d34cb9df8711430360aa5bb5","tid":1330094,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:10:51.000Z","msg":"蔡英文加分機會黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883e85f9ee6ed32de0671cbe8fd9179a492ee90a","tid":1330094,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"辛苦你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209b5bf20d5fe2dce225afbb73c303d9f09ec9b9","tid":1330094,"uid":105605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"香港愈黎愈多政治難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c2c9a8339ac9de6